# Desktop Pager
# PAGERHEAD is set in LocalVar.fvwm

Style "FvwmPager" NoTitle, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, StaysOntop, FixedPosition

*FvwmPager: Colorset * 23
*FvwmPagerFore    #000000
*FvwmPagerHilight #cccccc                                  
*FvwmPagerFont -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmPagerGeometry $[PAGER_GEOMETRY] 
*FvwmPagerLabel 0  $[PAGERHEAD]
*FvwmPagerSmallFont 5x8


